254
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:54,880
So the advice there, so this is for meetings 
and I want to talk about writing also,  

255
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:58,160
but for meetings, the advice here 
is before you get into a meeting,  

256
00:21:58,160 --> 00:22:02,720
