262
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:30,880
Yeah, I found this extremely powerful just 
like five minutes before you get into a  

263
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:33,440
meeting. And it could happen earlier 
in the day, right? It doesn't have to  

264
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:36,560
happen right before the meeting, or worst 
case, it's right before the meeting. Just,  

265
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:39,920
"Okay, what do I want to get out of this? 
What am I here? What do I want to say?"  

266
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:45,600
And just like giving your brain a little bit 
