306
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:59,200
it's confusing and you didn't include 
information you should have included,  

307
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:02,720
there's going to be a bunch of back and 
forth. All 15 of these people are reading  

308
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:07,680
this being like, "Okay, what do I do with this?"
Whereas if you had just taken another look at it,  

