360
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:54,480
meant. So it net, net takes longer. And I also 
think that it can be a little bit of a crutch,  

361
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:57,840
it can be a little bit lazy because 
you are telling yourself that you're  

362
00:30:57,840 --> 00:31:03,120
being concise when really, if you had to turn 
