364
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:13,920
didn't really know exactly what you meant. So as 
you're trying to turn it into a full sentence,  

365
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:18,240
you're actually needing to use brainpower.
So that's I think a great litmus test of,  

366
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:22,160
"Was that idea fully thought 
out?" Because if it was,  

367
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:27,600
you should be able to really quickly turn 
it into a complete sentence. And many times,  

368
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:32,160
you actually aren't. So I see people like 
basically think, "Oh, I want to make this  

369
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:35,680
easier to read, more skimmable. I'm just 
going to throw a bunch of formatting and  

